{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.1","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:1","prev_osis_id":"Isa.016.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Proph\u00e9tie contre Damas et Isra\u00ebl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-11: cf. (Am 1:3-5. J\u00e9 49:23-27.) \u00c9s 7:1-9; 8:1-4. (2 R 16:9; 17:1-6.) 2 Ch 30:1-11, 18.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Oracle sur Damas.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Voici, Damas ne sera plus une ville,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elle ne sera qu\u2019un monceau de ruines.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.2","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.16.14","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 16:14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.16.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.2","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:2","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Les villes d\u2019Aro\u00ebr sont abandonn\u00e9es,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elles sont livr\u00e9es aux troupeaux;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils s\u2019y couchent, et personne ne les effraie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.3","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.1","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.3","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:3","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>C\u2019en est fait de la forteresse d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et du royaume de Damas, et du reste de la Syrie:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il en sera comme de la gloire des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel des arm\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.4","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.2","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.4","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:4","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>En ce jour, la gloire de Jacob sera affaiblie,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et la graisse de sa chair s\u2019\u00e9vanouira.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.5","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.3","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.5","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:5","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il en sera comme quand le moissonneur r\u00e9colte les bl\u00e9s,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que son bras coupe les \u00e9pis;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme quand on ramasse les \u00e9pis,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dans la vall\u00e9e de Repha\u00efm.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.6","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.4","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.6","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:6","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il en restera un grappillage, comme quand on secoue l\u2019olivier,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Deux, trois olives, au haut de la cime,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Quatre, cinq, dans ses branches \u00e0 fruits,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.7","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.5","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.7","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:7","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>En ce jour, l\u2019homme regardera vers son cr\u00e9ateur,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ses yeux se tourneront vers le Saint d\u2019Isra\u00ebl;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.8","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.6","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.8","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:8","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il ne regardera plus vers les autels,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ouvrage de ses mains,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et il ne contemplera plus ce que ses doigts ont fabriqu\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Les idoles d\u2019Astart\u00e9 et les statues du soleil.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.9","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.7","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.9","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:9","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>En ce jour, ses villes fortes seront<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme des d\u00e9bris dans la for\u00eat et sur la cime des montagnes,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Abandonn\u00e9s devant les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ce sera un d\u00e9sert.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.10","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.8","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.10","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:10","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Car tu as oubli\u00e9 le Dieu de ton salut,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu ne t\u2019es pas souvenu du rocher de ton refuge.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Aussi tu as fait des plantations d\u2019agr\u00e9ment,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu as plant\u00e9 des ceps \u00e9trangers;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.11","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.9","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.11","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:11","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Lorsque tu les plantas, tu les entouras d\u2019une haie,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et bient\u00f4t tu les fis venir en fleurs.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais la r\u00e9colte a fui, au moment de la jouissance:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et la douleur est sans rem\u00e8de.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.10","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.12","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:12","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-14: cf. (\u00c9s 30:27-33; 37:33-38.) Ps 93:3, 4.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Oh! Quelle rumeur de peuples nombreux!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils mugissent comme mugit la mer.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Quel tumulte de nations!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elles grondent comme grondent les eaux puissantes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.13","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.11","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.13","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:13","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.017.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Les nations grondent comme grondent les grandes eaux\u2026<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il les menace, et elles fuient au loin,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Chass\u00e9es comme la balle des montagnes au souffle du vent,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme la poussi\u00e8re par un tourbillon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.14","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.14","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:14","prev_osis_id":"Isa.017.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.018.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.17.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Quand vient le soir, voici, c\u2019est une ruine soudaine;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Avant le matin, ils ne sont plus!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Voil\u00e0 le partage de ceux qui nous d\u00e9pouillent,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le sort de ceux qui nous pillent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.18.1","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.18.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.17.13","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 17:13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.17.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc23042b7.40407302');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc23042b7.40407302\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc23042b7.40407302","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc23042b7.40407302'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc23042b7.40407302\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}